$date
  2026-06-07T00:00:00.000Z
$end
$version
  WaveCrux Pro board demo fixture generator
$end
$comment
  Digilent Zybo Z7 out-of-box demo — individual per-bit signals.
  LED show: cylon / VU bar / chase / switch-mirror / expand / sparkle.
  Live peripherals: HDMI raster, audio sine, ADC, etc.
  Re-generate with `dart run tool/generate_board_demo_fixtures.dart`.
$end
$timescale 1 ns $end
$scope module top $end
$var wire 1 ! led0 $end
$var wire 1 " led1 $end
$var wire 1 # led2 $end
$var wire 1 $ led3 $end
$var wire 1 % sw0 $end
$var wire 1 & sw1 $end
$var wire 1 ' sw2 $end
$var wire 1 ( sw3 $end
$var wire 1 ) btn0 $end
$var wire 1 * btn1 $end
$var wire 1 + btn2 $end
$var wire 1 , btn3 $end
$var wire 1 - led_rgb_5 $end
$var wire 1 . led_rgb_6 $end
$var wire 16 / hdmi_in_data $end
$var wire 1 0 hdmi_in_pixel_clk $end
$var wire 1 1 hdmi_in_hsync $end
$var wire 1 2 hdmi_in_vsync $end
$var wire 1 3 hdmi_in_de $end
$var wire 16 4 hdmi_out_data $end
$var wire 1 5 hdmi_out_pixel_clk $end
$var wire 1 6 hdmi_out_hsync $end
$var wire 1 7 hdmi_out_vsync $end
$var wire 1 8 hdmi_out_de $end
$var wire 16 9 audio_codec_mic_in $end
$var wire 16 : audio_codec_headphone_out $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
